    "intro": {
      "title": "About OneDocs",
      "desc": "Smart document analysis",
      "paragraph1": "OneDocs is an AI-powered intelligent document analysis tool designed to help users quickly extract key information and organize knowledge from PDF documents. Whether it's news highlights, data analysis, or academic notes, OneDocs generates structured analysis results with one click.",
      "paragraph2": "Built with the Tauri v2 desktop framework and React 19, OneDocs provides a lightweight, smooth local experience. All document processing happens locally — your data is never uploaded to any third-party server, ensuring privacy and security.",
      "paragraph3": "By integrating multiple AI model providers, OneDocs supports flexible model switching to adapt to different scenarios. Four specialized analysis modes — News Overview, Data Analysis, STEM Quick Know, and Liberal Arts Richness — cover a wide range of document types from news to academia."
    },
